data.description: Price to sell Spectacular upgraded 3 beds 2 baths home plus private efficiency with its own kitchen and bathroom. (Huge Florida converted with a wall and easy to reopen). No HOA, pool for entertainment and huge backyard. This home can be used for airbnb. Redone entire floor and backyard for relaxation, bran new appliances, bran new stainless refrigerator, new stove, bran new air conditioning in 2021, brand new kitchen with granite countertop in 2022, freshly painted, new door, fenced all around, redone fixture and plumbing, carport.  Minutes from Ft Lauderdale airport, minutes from the beach and highways. Offer must accompany DU /mortgage approval. Priced below market for a quick sale! Seller may help buyer with some closing costs. Ready to move in! Call me for showing.
